amountPaid(address,uint256).details: Payment Client will reduce the total amount of tokens it will stock up by the given amount.This has to be called by a paymentProcessor.

params.amount: amount of tokens that have been paid out.
params.token: The token in which the payment was made.

params.collateralAmount_: The amount of collateral to spend.

params.depositAmount_: The amount of collateral to spend.
params.minAmountOut_: The minimum amount of tokens to receive.

calculatePurchaseReturn(uint256).details: This function takes into account any applicable buy fees before computing the         token amount to be minted. Revert when `_depositAmount` is zero.

params._depositAmount: The amount of tokens deposited by the user.

returns.mintAmount: The amount of new tokens that will be minted as a result of the deposit.

calculateSaleReturn(uint256).details: This function takes into account any applicable sell fees before computing the         collateral amount to be redeemed. Revert when `_depositAmount` is zero.

params._depositAmount: The amount of tokens deposited by the user.

returns.redeemAmount: The amount of collateral that will be redeemed as a result of the deposit.

closeSell().details: Only callable by the {Orchestrator_v1} admin.         Reverts if selling is already closed.

amountPaid(address,uint256).notice: Notifies the PaymentClient, that tokens have been paid out accordingly.

buy(uint256,uint256).notice: Buy tokens for the sender's address.

buyFor(address,uint256,uint256).notice: Buy tokens on behalf of a specified receiver address.

calculatePurchaseReturn(uint256).notice: Calculates the amount of tokens to be minted based on a given deposit amount.

calculateSaleReturn(uint256).notice: Calculates the amount of tokens to be redeemed based on a given deposit amount.

closeBuy().notice: Closes the buying functionality for the token.

closeSell().notice: Closes the selling functionality for the collateral.

depositReserve(uint256).notice: Allows depositing collateral to provide reserves for redemptions

getIssuanceToken().notice: Returns the address of the issuance token.

getMaxBuyFee().notice: Gets the maximum fee that can be charged for buy operations.

getMaxSellFee().notice: Gets the maximum fee that can be charged for sell operations.

getNextOrderId().notice: Gets the next available order ID

getOpenRedemptionAmount().notice: Gets the current open collateral redemption amount

getStaticPriceForBuying().notice: Calculates and returns the static price for buying the issuance token.

getStaticPriceForSelling().notice: Calculates and returns the static price for selling the issuance token.

grantModuleRole(bytes32,address).notice: Grants a module role to a target address.

grantModuleRoleBatched(bytes32,address[].notice: Grants a module role to multiple target addresses.

isDirectOperationsOnly().notice: Gets the direct operations only flag.

isTrustedForwarder(address).notice: Checks if the provided address is the trusted forwarder.

openBuy().notice: Opens the buying functionality for the token.

openSell().notice: Opens the selling functionality for the collateral.

outstandingTokenAmount(address).notice: Returns the total outstanding token payment amount.

paymentOrders().notice: Returns the list of outstanding payment orders.

projectCollateralFeeCollected().notice: Accumulated project trading fees collected from deposits made by users         when engaging with the bonding curve-based funding manager. Collected in collateral.

revokeModuleRole(bytes32,address).notice: Revokes a module role from a target address.

revokeModuleRoleBatched(bytes32,address[.notice: Revokes a module role from multiple target addresses.

sell(uint256,uint256).notice: Redeem collateral for the sender's address.

sellTo(address,uint256,uint256).notice: Redeem tokens and directs the proceeds to a specified receiver address.

setIsDirectOperationsOnly(bool).notice: Sets the direct operations only flag.

transferOrchestratorToken(address,uint25.notice: Transfer a specified amount of Tokens to a designated receiver address.

withdrawProjectCollateralFee(address,uin.notice: Withdraw project collateral fee to the receiver address.
